            h2 Setup

            .row-fluid
              .span4
                h4.feature-title Setup
                p Simply serve a html file from your server.
                p Example file is in the download!

              .span8
                .feature
                  :markdown
                    markup:

                        <!doctype html>
                        <html lang="en">
                        <head>
                          <!-- Application styles -->
                          <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/i18nextWT.css">
                        </head>

                        <body>
                          <!-- Optional Header -->
                          <div class="header">
                            <div class="header-inner"></div>
                          </div>

                          <div class="main">
                            <div class="main-inner"></div>
                          </div>

                          <!-- Optional Footer -->
                          <div class="footer">
                            <div class="footer-inner"></div>
                          </div>

                          <!-- Application source -->
                          <script src="js/i18nextWT.js"></script>

                          <!-- Initalization callback for configuration -->
                          <script language="javascipt" type="text/javascript">
                            i18nextWT_onready = function(wt) {

                              wt.config(
                                {
                                  languages: ["en-US", "de", "fr", "dev"],
                                  namespaces: ["ns.common", "ns.special"],
                                  resGetPath: "locales/resources.json?lng=__lng__&ns=__ns__",
                                  resChangePath: "locales/change/__lng__/__ns__",
                                  resRemovePath: "locales/remove/__lng__/__ns__",
                                  fallbackLng: "dev",
                                  dynamicLoad: true
                                }
                              )

                              wt.start();
                            };
                          </script>
                        </body>
                        </html>

                  .alert.alert-info.feature-description
                    h6 Important hint:
                    p Be sure your server serves following routes like you set them in options:
                      ul
                        li 
                          strong resGetPath:
                          p route from where resources are loaded (with dynamicLoad = true |Â false)
                         li 
                          strong resChangePath:
                          p route to post changes to (serverside update)
                        li 
                          strong resGetPath:
                          p route to post removing of key/value (serverside remove)

            .row-fluid
              .span4
                h4.feature-title Add Additional languages

              .span8
                .feature
                    p i18next-webtranslate comes with english and german translations.
                    :markdown
                      To add additional languages call in the __i18nextWT_onready__ callback:

                          <!-- Initalization callback for configuration -->
                          <script language="javascipt" type="text/javascript">
                            i18nextWT_onready = function(wt) {

                              wt.config(
                                {
                                  languages: ["en-US", "de", "fr", "dev"],
                                  // ...
                                }
                              )

                              wt.addResourceSet("en-US", {
                               layout: {
                                  header: {
                                    language: "english" // will be displayed in language switch
                                  }
                                },
                                editor: {
                                  // ...
                                }
                              });

                              wt.start();
                            };
                          </script>

                  .alert.alert-info.feature-description
                    p 
                      | For updated list of needed resource keys have a look 
                      a(href='https://github.com/jamuhl/i18next-webtranslate/blob/master/client/app/resources.js') here
                      |.


